{"tid":1554753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連儂牆]最新文宣，嚇到班港豬驚","createTime":"2019-09-09T05:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:45:57.000Z","uid":295483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1694c80f8d54e27e4413132bb98892afbe8ce3e1","tid":1554753,"uid":295483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣文宣fb又好ig又好一定要輸出<br />\n我哋嘅文宣就係要放大點解我哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">寧願攬炒</span></strong></span>，香港仲有好多港豬仲係着重社會唔好亂，唔好搞亂佢個經濟最緊要唔好影響到佢自己<br />\n就係要放大依家唔抗爭，將來點樣會影響到佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新疆集中營</span></span>，要輸出共產黨真係咩都做得出，而家已經有過百萬維吾爾族人被收押集中營，都是我哋香港土生土長嗰啲都不能幸免(重中之重，可以話放大嚇鳩佢亦都可以講係事實）因為佢哋呢一班人仲未識驚<br />\n仲有文宣方面<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跳閘</span></span>都好緊要，就係因為黨鐵同黑警合作，連831太子站CCTV都唔交出嚟，唔俾公眾一個知情，呢樣野係關乎人命，黑警濫捕、濫打、濫拉嘅情況下，黨鐵都去維護，所以示威者先會跳閘表示抗議，亦都係依方面加強大大力全民跳閘<br />\n亦都係因為黨鐵，亦都要俾啲師奶阿叔知道我哋要開始<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買罷食黨鐵嘅商場</span></strong></span><br />\n最最最最重要就係放大有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲搞事時千祈唔好報警，</span></strong></span>比佢哋知道好多單原告都變被告，打人果個就同啲黑警攬頭攬頸，邊個報警就係鬼，到時得兩個方法可以解決，一就係好大愛咁影完相教訓佢一輪就放佢走，二就最小限度鍚春袋錫到佢爛先走<br />\n呢啲文宣要大量貼去連儂牆，因為真係仲有好多唔上Facebook IG嘅人<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"dc16da3ab758005b1f345a6026f6a2ac433f4b41","tid":1554753,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a9f1f55c0c985691331b820b22222c8a45490cb","tid":1554753,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:17:19.000Z","msg":"推 一人一文宣呀<br />\n大家接龍出圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3if5mdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3if5mdN.jpg&h=8cbca400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zvfw1eC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvfw1eC.jpg&h=9c3260fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a022a6b79da206ced951ef7b8a79a7584c98624","tid":1554753,"uid":266536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:18:13.000Z","msg":"For 痴地板用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7Q5sfB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7Q5sfB.jpg&h=b5307f9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa66131141064cf5535357a59dedafa88e996363","tid":1554753,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3DVQV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3DVQV6.jpg&h=2c40e53e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以貼高啲就唔會咁快畀人撕"},{"pid":"b77d59797af7743b27d5179860b1f513d42c0581","tid":1554753,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wgHSTbx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwgHSTbx.jpg&h=c3700e45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N4WHvYe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4WHvYe.jpg&h=81997614&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpMcTbA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpMcTbA.jpg&h=5f5169ea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}